s\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Greeted by a sea of adoring fans, Jin led the relay at the iconic Louvre Museum, making it a memorable evening for all.\", \"from\": 551, \"to\": 670, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 585, \"end\": 588, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Seok-jin\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 3.1076625532583454e-13, \"text\": \"Jin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Seok-jin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Seok-jin\"}, {\"begin\": 617, \"end\": 630, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louvre\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Louvre Museum\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\", \"Q33506\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louvre\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louvre\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The event began around 8 p.m., with crowds of BTS fans, affectionately known as ARMY, gathering to catch a glimpse of their favourite star.\", \"from\": 672, \"to\": 811, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 718, \"end\": 721, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BTS\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7967276991652362e-28, \"text\": \"BTS\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q215380\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BTS\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BTS\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Signs reading \\\"Welcome, Seok-jin, I Love You,\\\" \\\"Run, Seok-jin,\\\" and \\\"Good luck, Seok-jin\\\" adorned the area.\", \"from\": 813, \"to\": 920, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This was alongside fluttering Korean national flags.\", \"from\": 921, \"to\": 973, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 951, \"end\": 957, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Korean_language\", \"score\": 0.9993987974752414, \"rank\": 0.00042671052599752533, \"text\": \"Korean\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Korean_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Korean_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Jin, whose birth name is Kim Seok-jin, was met with overwhelming support, according toBillboard.\", \"from\": 975, \"to\": 1071, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 975, \"end\": 978, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Seok-jin\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 3.1076625532583454e-13, \"text\": \"Jin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Seok-jin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Seok-jin\"}, {\"begin\": 1000, \"end\": 1012, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Seok-jin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.281476897024777e-45, \"text\": \"Kim Seok-jin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Seok-jin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Seok-jin\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As Jin emerged from the torch relay centre, the crowd erupted in cheers, chanting his name.\", \"from\": 1073, \"to\": 1164, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1076, \"end\": 1079, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Seok-jin\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 3.1076625532583454e-13, \"text\": \"Jin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Seok-jin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Seok-jin\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With a shy smile, he waved to his fans, acknowledging their love and support.\", \"from\": 1166, \"to\": 1243, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Escorted by police, Jin then moved to Rue de Rivoli, where he was handed the torch.\", \"from\": 1245, \"to\": 1328, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1265, \"end\": 1268, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Seok-jin\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 3.1076625532583454e-13, \"text\": \"Jin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Seok-jin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Seok-jin\"}, {\"begin\": 1283, \"end\": 1296, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rue_de_Rivoli\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rue de Rivoli\", \"types\": [\"Q34442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rue_de_Rivoli\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rue_de_Rivoli\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He ran about 200 meters before returning it to the relay centre, according to theDaily Guardian.\", \"from\": 1330, \"to\": 1426, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The event coincided with Bastille Day, adding to the festive atmosphere.\", \"from\": 1428, \"to\": 1500, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I feel extremely honoured to have been able to participate in today's torch relay,\\\" Jin said afterwards.\", \"from\": 1502, \"to\": 1607, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1587, \"end\": 1590, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Seok-jin\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 3.1076625532583454e-13, \"text\": \"Jin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Seok-jin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Seok-jin\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This was according to Hybe, the parent company of his agency, BigHit Music.\", \"from\": 1608, \"to\": 1683, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1630, \"end\": 1634, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hybe_Corporation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.720725891400825e-28, \"text\": \"Hybe\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hybe_Corporation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hybe_Corporation\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I sincerely thank ARMY and all the fans who made it possible for me to carry the torch.\\\"\", \"from\": 1685, \"to\": 1774, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Jin, now 31, recently completed his mandatory military service, becoming the first BTS member to do so.\", \"from\": 1776, \"to\": 1879, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1776, \"end\": 1779, \"titl