", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_flame\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_flame\"}, {\"begin\": 2146, \"end\": 2151, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.0917185614180975e-18, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2204, \"end\": 2210, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9642204466684511, \"rank\": 0.03694809784376557, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It will then come back to Paris for the grand opening ceremony on 26 July.\", \"from\": 2268, \"to\": 2342, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2294, \"end\": 2299, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.0917185614180975e-18, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The excitement among fans was palpable.\", \"from\": 2344, \"to\": 2383, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Marie, a dedicated BTS fan who travelled from Lyon to witness the event, said, \\\"Seeing Jin carry the torch was a dream come true.\\\"\", \"from\": 2385, \"to\": 2515, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2404, \"end\": 2407, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BTS\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7967276991652362e-28, \"text\": \"BTS\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q215380\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BTS\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BTS\"}, {\"begin\": 2431, \"end\": 2435, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lyon\", \"score\": 0.9999999996998667, \"rank\": 3.0016467675743823e-10, \"text\": \"Lyon\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lyon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lyon\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"His smile lit up the whole street.\\\"\", \"from\": 2517, \"to\": 2553, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Another fan, Emma, held a sign that read, \\\"Run, Seok-jin.\\\"\", \"from\": 2555, \"to\": 2613, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2568, \"end\": 2572, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_Swan\", \"score\": 0.9974711206010203, \"rank\": 0.002533531956709733, \"text\": \"Emma\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_Swan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_Swan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She shared, \\\"I have followed BTS for years, and seeing Jin here in Paris, representing the Olympics, is incredible.\", \"from\": 2615, \"to\": 2730, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2644, \"end\": 2647, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BTS\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7967276991652362e-28, \"text\": \"BTS\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q215380\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BTS\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BTS\"}, {\"begin\": 2670, \"end\": 2673, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Seok-jin\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 3.1076625532583454e-13, \"text\": \"Jin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Seok-jin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Seok-jin\"}, {\"begin\": 2682, \"end\": 2687, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.0917185614180975e-18, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's a moment I will never forget.\\\"\", \"from\": 2731, \"to\": 2766, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Jin's participation in the torch relay is a testament to his global influence and the power of BTS's music and message.\", \"from\": 2768, \"to\": 2887, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2768, \"end\": 2771, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Seok-jin\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 3.1076625532583454e-13, \"text\": \"Jin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Seok-jin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Seok-jin\"}, {\"begin\": 2863, \"end\": 2866, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BTS\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7967276991652362e-28, \"text\": \"BTS\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q215380\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BTS\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BTS\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The group, known for their positive and uplifting songs, has a massive following worldwide.\", \"from\": 2889, \"to\": 2980, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Jin's appearance in Paris not only thrilled fans but also showcased the unifying power of music and sport.\", \"from\": 2982, \"to\": 3088, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2982, \"end\": 2985, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Seok-jin\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 3.1076625532583454e-13, \"text\": \"Jin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Seok-jin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Seok-jin\"}, {\"begin\": 3002, \"end\": 3007, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.0917185614180975e-18, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As the torch relay continues, anticipation builds for the opening ceremony of the 2024 Paris Summer Olympics.\", \"from\": 3090, \"to\": 3199, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Jin'srolein the relay will undoubtedly be remembered as one of its highlights.\", \"from\": 3201, \"to\": 3279, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"His humble and heartfelt presence left a lasting impression on all who witnessed it.\", \"from\": 3281, \"to\": 3365, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In the words of one fan, \\\"Jin running with the torch is a symbol of hope and unity.\", \"from\": 3367, \"to\": 3450, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3393, \"end\": 3396, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Seok-jin\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 3.1076625532583454e-13, \"text\": \"Jin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Seok-jin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Seok-jin\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It shows that no matter where we come from, we can come together to celebrate something beautiful.\\\"\", \"from\": 3452, \"to\": 3551, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"With the Olympics just around the corner, Jin's contribution to the torch relay has set a high bar.\", \"from\": 3553, \"to\": 3652, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3595, \"end\": 3598, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Seok-jin\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 3.1076625532583454e-13, \"text\": \"Jin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Seok-jin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Seok-jin\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His performance was not just a run, but a moment of connection and joy for fans around the world.\", \"from\": 3654, \"to\": 3751, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"His participation highlighted the intersection of pop culture and international sport, bringing immense visibility to the Olympics among younger generations.\", \"from\": 3753, \"to\": 3910, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Fans worldwide felt a sense of pride and connection, as Jin's involvement symbolised unity and perseverance.\", \"from\": 3912, \"to\": 4020, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3968, \"end\": 3971, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Seok-jin\", \"s